Title: 025: Women in STEM, Bench Science to Data Science and Data and Medical Ethics w/ Kimberly Deas
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with Data Analyst Kimberly Deas. You will get to listen to a discussion about women in STEM, know how being into bench science field could get you to data science and be able to learn about data and medical ethics.
